Having said that, you may be able to bypass some of the calls to
dbinom and dpois because you are evaluating a sequence of such values.
 Evaluating dbinom or dpois for a particular value needs to be done
carefully (i.e. not according to the formulas given in most textbooks)
but updating from one value to the next in a sequence is fairly easy
and can be done with the naive formula.


